      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"Digital Twin\"  +  [Live \u00b7 DATASET] badge  +  [N skills] badge  +  [N interactions] badge\nStudent: <uid>  \u00b7  Last interaction <date> (from timeline[last].timestamp)\nmasteryDelta = avg(last snapshot mastery) \u2212 avg(first snapshot mastery)\n  shown as \u00b1XX.XX% (emerald if \u2265 0, red if < 0)  \u00b7  hidden if timeline.length < 2",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Digital Twin\"  +  [Live \u00b7 DATASET] badge  +  [N skills] badge  +  [N interactions] badge\nStudent: <uid>  \u00b7  Last interaction <date> (from timeline[last].timestamp)\nmasteryDelta = avg(last snapshot mastery) \u2212 avg(first snapshot mastery)\n  shown as \u00b1XX.XX% (emerald if \u2265 0, red if < 0)  \u00b7  hidden if timeline.length < 2",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
