      "updated": 1703000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "masteryList = mastery.map((m,i)=>({skillIdx:i, name:skillNameMap[i], mastery:m})).sort((a,b)=>b.mastery-a.mastery)\n\nLayout: dual-column grid \u00b7 max-height 520px \u00b7 overflow-y-auto\nPer row: progress bar (w-20 h-2) + percentage (mono w-10) + skill name (truncated)\n\nColor thresholds:\n  m >= 0.80  \u2192 #22c55e  (Strong)\n  m >= 0.60  \u2192 #84cc16  (Good)\n  m >= 0.40  \u2192 #f59e0b  (Developing)\n  m <  0.40  \u2192 #ef4444  (At risk)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "masteryList = mastery.map((m,i)=>({skillIdx:i, name:skillNameMap[i], mastery:m})).sort((a,b)=>b.mastery-a.mastery)\n\nLayout: dual-column grid \u00b7 max-height 520px \u00b7 overflow-y-auto\nPer row: progress bar (w-20 h-2) + percentage (mono w-10) + skill name (truncated)\n\nColor thresholds:\n  m >= 0.80  \u2192 #22c55e  (Strong)\n  m >= 0.60  \u2192 #84cc16  (Good)\n  m >= 0.40  \u2192 #f59e0b  (Developing)\n  m <  0.40  \u2192 #ef4444  (At risk)",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
