      "updated": 1703000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "riskAlerts = mastery\n  .filter(m => m < THRESHOLD)\n  .sort by mastery asc  \u00b7  top 10\n\nPer alert: Badge (HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW) + skill name + mastery %\n  HIGH:   mastery < 0.3  \u2192  variant=destructive\n  MEDIUM: mastery < 0.4  \u2192  variant=default\n  LOW:    mastery < 0.5  \u2192  variant=secondary\n\n\u2713 If no alerts: \"All N skills at or above 50%\"",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "riskAlerts = mastery\n  .filter(m => m < THRESHOLD)\n  .sort by mastery asc  \u00b7  top 10\n\nPer alert: Badge (HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW) + skill name + mastery %\n  HIGH:   mastery < 0.3  \u2192  variant=destructive\n  MEDIUM: mastery < 0.4  \u2192  variant=default\n  LOW:    mastery < 0.5  \u2192  variant=secondary\n\n\u2713 If no alerts: \"All N skills at or above 50%\"",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
